{"tid":1736314,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好再屌佢地投降","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T18:25:25.000Z","uid":10679,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"705f73f366227cf2476b6e6a2f1201583b9ad598","tid":1736314,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"1. 埋大入面仲有二百個手足（from 612reminder），唔係全部投哂降<br />\n2. 投得降嘅唔係受左傷就十八歲以下<br />\n3. 吹得雞開post死守嘅，相信都唔會投降，一定一係仲係埋大入面，一係就成功走左果100個嚟"},{"pid":"69fd100d627cd6f58050bc8583a7f90053410a09","tid":1736314,"uid":271617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"行出去＝自首，比人捉＝可疑"},{"pid":"6604c8eabb65c9c63ad44d04124d2b5a41f6cb69","tid":1736314,"uid":141625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"係 唔該大家唔好再屌 有好多傷曬 根本打又唔係偷走又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8382359ce81e6feb34368790e82e6ff195560e8","tid":1736314,"uid":10679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"唔投都投左，不割蓆"},{"pid":"b324e4e24482239a2d585fb397884c3db19696f9","tid":1736314,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b56894f35e8bd250bdd3585ca3b93c67f049034","tid":1736314,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89785df4f00354ae41ed444358c94892b653bc80","tid":1736314,"uid":67822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後邊個想屌人、互屌、對自己人有不滿，就望住呢堆相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471935</a><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"179ef07fe8f932acc1fbfb2a6479e20a442c6192","tid":1736314,"uid":32215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"推 不分化"},{"pid":"7a164c12fac6b30453023b54283d52d377e3cfd8","tid":1736314,"uid":260369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"我地可以做既係支持佢地<br />\n如果可以就監察住佢地會唔會被消失啊、提堂啊，睇下佢地需唔需要任何支援<br />\n<br />\n無乜好屌，人人threshold唔同，始終我地係由意志而匯聚，每個人想法不盡相同。"},{"pid":"fb8d8e0df615f47e7dedbbe2daf2241d155e0b75","tid":1736314,"uid":243588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"咁呢個係佢地既選擇<br />\n我覺得要尊重<br />\n但係必須要話比佢知 --&gt; 由佢自己權衡輕重<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地日日都會加油黎救你地架<br />\n要撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8814f6674b6e2eb65a8a29e8f2ddff73be69e7f8","tid":1736314,"uid":209307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢地都係曾經打生打死既手足，每個決定都有險，人人都有佢地難處，尊重佢地！<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆！<br />\n一日手足，一世手足！</span>"},{"pid":"3d18a2253dbdd12e0164ec0bfba127d7238f0a50","tid":1736314,"uid":235119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"a5ce9d66234be088c90d4775caf39bde0c90ab87","tid":1736314,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"唔投都投左，不割蓆"},{"pid":"e7f1f483c05ef9f4a9bd9151dfe4f6aacea079a2","tid":1736314,"uid":170930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"絕對相信佢地係堅守到最後一刻先投降。係受傷同不得已情況下投降完全無損佢地榮譽！<br />\n<br />\n覺得投降一定係恥辱係華人一種劣質文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112c2572e4fac92d9644f3b99f7ddd359f4446f9","tid":1736314,"uid":248364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"原來仲有200...即係話已經比左機會你投左降，入面200個到時捉到就一定暴動....."},{"pid":"3f650d7c6e727dc180f6990da28a8bd357e3b803","tid":1736314,"uid":149849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"好心大家比啲尊重啦<br />\n困係理大個個又唔係班冷氣軍師<br />\n憑咩屌手足？"},{"pid":"5a735b545627fde9365ac1dad9f3b8c0852f4759","tid":1736314,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"唔投都投左，不割蓆"},{"pid":"c3492d45a4f92a13901614436517df8f84194b96","tid":1736314,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:45:23.000Z","msg":"唉手足自己嘅決定 只能夠尊重<br />\n佢地本人一定都好難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十年啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0100041329f59767813a09a7f1a247fd065798a","tid":1736314,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited